data.description: This Arthur Rutenburg home has it all! NEW CEMENT TiLE ROOF (2021), NEW TRANE A/C (2023), NEW STAINLESS APPLIANCE PACKAGE (2023), NEW FLOORING BEDROOMS/OFFICE (2021), LANAI RESURFACE (in progress), DESIGNER PRIMARY BATH (2023), PLUS A ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY, AND an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 3.2%! You will love living in the Verandah, a 24 hour manned gate community with tons of amenities. Shady Bend may be the most desired street in the community and you are just steps away from a walking/biking trail that leads right to the pool, fitness center, restaurants, tennis, pickelball, shaded kids playground and kayaking the Orange River! And don't forget the dog park. This beautiful home has many aspects of new construction, but it also has charm, character and warmth that new construction may lack. Plantation shutters, invisible corner sliders, tall ceilings, bullnose corners, exquisite granite counters, bay window in master, upgraded baseboards, crown moulding, ceiling fans in all main rooms, disable friendly, work bench, garage cabinets and so much more to list! Come and see for yourself. Assumable mortgage through New American Funding. Home warranty through Home Tech. Don't miss this one
